{"type":"article","id":7170,"title":"四中全会前夕，朱镕基通过公开信发声挑战包子","uid":3685,"topics":[281,120,1253,136,779,424],"contents":"四中全会前夕朱镕基发表公开信，<br>\n对习的反“改革开放”路线提出挑战。<br>\n<br>\n公开信显示了中南海的分裂，<br>\n朱镕基、王岐山、俞正声抱团组成“金融帮“。<br>\n15省开始配置“金融副省长”，<br>\n显示“金融帮“开始事实上控制了中国地方政府。<br>\n<br>\nhttps://t.co/RtsTCuaEE3<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EH0hbd4WkAAYWI7?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EH0hbd4WkAAYWI7?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EH0hbd4WkAAYWI7?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-10-26","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}